metadata.description: EAC scarcity analysis: SSS baselines, corporate demand scenarios, scarcity classifications, clean premiums
metadata.framework: SSS = mandatory/non-bypassable procurement (RPS/CES, public ownership, rate-base, state nuclear programs)

CAISO.notes: Diablo Canyon is fixed SSS (state-supported indefinitely). SB 100 RPS drives renewable growth.

ERCOT.notes: Minimal RPS, mostly merchant renewables, deregulated market

PJM.notes: Mixed: state RPSs + merchant nuclear (post-NJ ZEC expiry)

NYISO.notes: NY ZEC extended through 2049, CLCPA 70% by 2030

NEISO.notes: CT Millstone PPA, MA/CT CES, some merchant hydro/wind
